      "comment": "WALTZING BRUTE (1) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish third, beaten 1.5 lengths, (16.63) at this track. Capable of going well again. SUN IN CUBA (7) has been out of the placings at her last couple but on the winners' heels when placing three back (19.36) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Well placed here and can atone this time. FIRE UP MARK (2) did a good job to finish third last time out over 390m at Ballarat (22.43) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot. Can find the frame this time. ARCANA (4) could manage only sixth but in a convincing 16.70 latest. Among the chances.",
